      "id": "b-002",
      "mode": "explain",
      "speakerNote": "Warm, personal. Share your own experience at the noodle stall. Make the viewer feel like they're there with you.",
      "imageRef": "img-001",
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "l-0004",
          "lang": "en",
          "english": "When I first moved to Bangkok, there was this noodle stall near my apartment. Every morning, the same aunty would shout at me — สั่งอะไรดีคะ — and I had no idea what to say. I just pointed at the picture.",
          "display": "immediate",
          "spoken": true
        },
        {
          "id": "l-0005",
          "lang": "th",
          "thai": "สั่งอะไรดีคะ",
          "translit": "sàng a-rai dii khá",
          "display": "immediate",
          "spoken": true
        },
        {
          "id": "l-0006",
          "lang": "en",
          "english": "By the end of this video, you won't need to point. You'll order in Thai, ask for recommendations, tell them how spicy you want it, and get the bill — all in Thai.",
          "display": "immediate",
          "spoken": true
        }
      ]
